{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.11.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.11.1","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 11:1","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.010.027,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.011.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Sa\u00fcl vainqueur des Ammonites<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-11: cf. (Jg 11. 1 S 31:11-13.) 1 S 10:7.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.11.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>Nachasch, l\u2019Ammonite, vint assi\u00e9ger Jab\u00e8s en Galaad. Tous les habitants de Jab\u00e8s dirent \u00e0 Nachasch: Traite alliance avec nous, et nous te servirons.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.11","name":"1 Samuel 11","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.11"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.11.2","name":"1 Samuel 11:2","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.11.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.10.27","name":"1 Samuel 10:27","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.10.27"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.11.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.11.2","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 11:2","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.011.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.011.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.11.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>Mais Nachasch, l\u2019Ammonite, leur r\u00e9pondit: Je traiterai avec vous \u00e0 la condition que je vous cr\u00e8ve \u00e0 tous l\u2019\u0153il droit, et que j\u2019imprime ainsi un opprobre sur tout Isra\u00ebl.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.11","name":"1 Samuel 11","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.11"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.11.3","name":"1 Samuel 11:3","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.11.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.11.1","name":"1 Samuel 11:1","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.11.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.11.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.11.3","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 11:3","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.011.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.011.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.11.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>Les anciens de Jab\u00e8s lui dirent: Accorde-nous une tr\u00eave de sept jours, afin que nous envoyions des messagers dans tout le territoire d\u2019Isra\u00ebl; et s\u2019il n\u2019y a personne qui nous secoure, nous nous rendrons \u00e0 toi.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.11","name":"1 Samuel 11","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.11"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.11.4","name":"1 Samuel 11:4","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.11.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.11.2","name":"1 Samuel 11:2","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.11.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.11.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.11.4","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 11:4","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.011.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.011.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.11.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>Les messagers arriv\u00e8rent \u00e0 Guibea de Sa\u00fcl, et dirent ces choses aux oreilles du peuple. Et tout le peuple \u00e9leva la voix, et pleura.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.11","name":"1 Samuel 11","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.11"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.11.5","name":"1 Samuel 11:5","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.11.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.11.3","name":"1 Samuel 11:3","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.11.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.11.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.11.5","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 11:5","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.011.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.011.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.11.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>Et voici, Sa\u00fcl revenait des champs, derri\u00e8re ses b\u0153ufs, et il dit: Qu\u2019a donc le peuple pour pleurer? On lui raconta ce qu\u2019avaient dit ceux de Jab\u00e8s.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.11","name":"1 Samuel 11","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.11"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.11.6","name":"1 Samuel 11:6","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.11.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.11.4","name":"1 Samuel 11:4","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.11.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.11.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.11.6","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 11:6","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.011.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.011.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.11.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>D\u00e8s que Sa\u00fcl eut entendu ces choses, il fut saisi par l\u2019esprit de Dieu, et sa col\u00e8re s\u2019enflamma fortement.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.11","name":"1 Samuel 11","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.11"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.11.7","name":"1 Samuel 11:7","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.11.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.11.5","name":"1 Samuel 11:5","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.11.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.11.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.11.7","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 11:7","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.011.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.011.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.11.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>Il prit une paire de b\u0153ufs, et les coupa en morceaux, qu\u2019il envoya par les messagers dans tout le territoire d\u2019Isra\u00ebl, en disant: Quiconque ne marchera pas \u00e0 la suite de Sa\u00fcl et de Samuel, aura ses b\u0153ufs trait\u00e9s de la m\u00eame mani\u00e8re. La terreur de l\u2019\u00c9ternel s\u2019empara du peuple, qui se mit en marche comme un seul homme.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.11","name":"1 Samuel 11","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.11"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.11.8","name":"1 Samuel 11:8","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.11.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.11.6","name":"1 Samuel 11:6","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.11.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.11.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.11.8","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 11:8","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.011.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.011.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.11.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>Sa\u00fcl en fit la revue \u00e0 B\u00e9zek; les enfants d\u2019Isra\u00ebl \u00e9taient trois cent mille, et les hommes de Juda trente mille.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.11","name":"1 Samuel 11","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.11"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.11.9","name":"1 Samuel 11:9","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.11.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.11.7","name":"1 Samuel 11:7","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.11.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.11.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.11.9","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 11:9","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.011.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.011.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.11.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>Ils dirent aux messagers qui \u00e9taient venus: Vous parlerez ainsi aux habitants de Jab\u00e8s en Galaad: Demain vous aurez du secours, quand le soleil sera dans sa chaleur. Les messagers port\u00e8rent cette nouvelle \u00e0 ceux de Jab\u00e8s, qui furent remplis de joie;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.11","name":"1 Samuel 11","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.11"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.11.10","name":"1 Samuel 11:10","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.11.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.11.8","name":"1 Samuel 11:8","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.11.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.11.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.11.10","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 11:10","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.011.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.011.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.11.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>et qui dirent aux Ammonites: Demain nous nous rendrons \u00e0 vous, et vous nous traiterez comme bon vous semblera.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.11","name":"1 Samuel 11","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.11"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.11.11","name":"1 Samuel 11:11","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.11.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.11.9","name":"1 Samuel 11:9","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.11.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.11.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.11.11","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 11:11","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.011.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.011.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.11.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>Le lendemain, Sa\u00fcl divisa le peuple en trois corps. Ils p\u00e9n\u00e9tr\u00e8rent dans le camp des Ammonites \u00e0 la veille du matin, et ils les battirent jusqu\u2019\u00e0 la chaleur du jour. Ceux qui \u00e9chapp\u00e8rent furent dispers\u00e9s, et il n\u2019en resta pas deux ensemble.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.11","name":"1 Samuel 11","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.11"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.11.12","name":"1 Samuel 11:12","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.11.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.11.10","name":"1 Samuel 11:10","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.11.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.11.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.11.12","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 11:12","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.011.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.011.013,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 12-15: cf. 1 S 10:17-27. 1 Ch 29:21, 22.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.11.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>Le peuple dit \u00e0 Samuel: Qui est-ce qui disait: Sa\u00fcl r\u00e9gnera-t-il sur nous? Livrez ces gens, et nous les ferons mourir.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.11","name":"1 Samuel 11","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.11"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.11.13","name":"1 Samuel 11:13","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.11.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.11.11","name":"1 Samuel 11:11","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.11.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.11.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.11.13","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 11:13","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.011.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.011.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.11.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>Mais Sa\u00fcl dit: Personne ne sera mis \u00e0 mort en ce jour, car aujourd\u2019hui l\u2019\u00c9ternel a op\u00e9r\u00e9 une d\u00e9livrance en Isra\u00ebl.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.11","name":"1 Samuel 11","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.11"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.11.14","name":"1 Samuel 11:14","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.11.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.11.12","name":"1 Samuel 11:12","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.11.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.11.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.11.14","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 11:14","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.011.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.011.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.11.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>Et Samuel dit au peuple: Venez, et allons \u00e0 Guilgal, pour y confirmer la royaut\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.11","name":"1 Samuel 11","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.11"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.11.15","name":"1 Samuel 11:15","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.11.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.11.13","name":"1 Samuel 11:13","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.11.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.11.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.11.15","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 11:15","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.011.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.012.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.11.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>Tout le peuple se rendit \u00e0 Guilgal, et ils \u00e9tablirent Sa\u00fcl pour roi, devant l\u2019\u00c9ternel, \u00e0 Guilgal. L\u00e0, ils offrirent des sacrifices d\u2019actions de gr\u00e2ces devant l\u2019\u00c9ternel; et l\u00e0, Sa\u00fcl et tous les hommes d\u2019Isra\u00ebl se livr\u00e8rent \u00e0 de grandes r\u00e9jouissances.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.11","name":"1 Samuel 11","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.11"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.12.1","name":"1 Samuel 12:1","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.12.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.11.14","name":"1 Samuel 11:14","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.11.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fba5c6c41.63591685');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fba5c6c41.63591685\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81fba5c6c41.63591685","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefined'){ _BAPI.t('5af81fba5c6c41.63591685'); }","fums_noscript":"<img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fba5c6c41.63591685\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/>"}}}